=== 防護力 ===
如同[[T-14|T-14主力戰車]]，T-15步兵戰車是以[[反应装甲|反應式裝甲]]作為其主要防護的<ref name="globalsecurity"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/russia/t-15.htm "T-15 (Object 149) heavy infantry combat vehicle"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/russia/t-15.htm |date=20190821154052 }}. ''globalsecurity.org''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref>。另外，T-15亦搭載了與[[T-14|T-14]]相同的<span>Afganit（[[俄語|俄語]]：Афганит）主動防禦系統。</span><ref name="defenseupdate20150509"><cite class="citation web">[http://defense-update.com/20150509_t14-t15_analysis.html "New Russian Armor; First analysis: Armata"]. ''defense-update.com''. 9 May 2015<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref><ref name="defenseupdate20150509"><cite class="citation web">[http://defense-update.com/20150509_t14-t15_analysis.html "New Russian Armor; First analysis: Armata"]. ''defense-update.com''. 9 May 2015<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref>

